{"tid":785680,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳秀雯為智叔再拍劇 #ViuTV #教束","createTime":"2018-08-19T11:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T07:47:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f9636114e7448f9490dfeed9ec0c7bdfd32718","tid":785680,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180819/20479570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F20479570&d=gTn8TklaZDEjTPqfaWz9jdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ddc6ec46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F20479570&h=7273c82c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180819/20479570</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月19日 <br />\n<br />\n陳秀雯為智叔再拍劇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180819/large/19ec3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180819%2Flarge%2F19ec3p2a.jpg&h=52c816e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳秀雯及廖啟智昨日於坑口一間中學，為ViuTV新劇《教束》進行拜神，差不多有九年沒有拍劇的秀雯指，今次接拍原因是再跟智叔合作，另外因為是校園劇，她說：「我以前睇好多校園片，我覺得每個年代都要拍，因為70、80、90同2000年代校園都唔一樣。」劇情主要在學校發生，因此暑假結束前便拍畢，秀雯說：「因為學校全部都係日頭戲，從來都未試過咁舒服。」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n香香為老公鑽研廚藝<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n何紫綸搞選美失眠"},{"pid":"c0b43fbe4bc71890dc89e5cab35be311c5aa1c96","tid":785680,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"兩個都好好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276809461081bbd0af185893ce21c79d5ff6844d","tid":785680,"uid":29702,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:38:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80f89228ba186112b6e1e831df86523d6bba0919","tid":785680,"uid":134367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"陳秀雯當年好有氣質"},{"pid":"cdd8ed0275bedbfd9f2caf8dfd17d43753baaf90","tid":785680,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"音:教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0fbb24063d340204d64c57510dd4fd4ad17696","tid":785680,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"276809461081bbd0af185893ce21c79d5ff6844d","tid":785680,"uid":29702,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c0b43fbe4bc71890dc89e5cab35be311c5aa1c96","tid":785680,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"兩個都好好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:38:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"佢拍無線同佢返亞視果期都係同級演技<br />\n<br />\n睇埋大塊田同幾個亞視過去 只係個色較光D已經驅咗陣味<br />\n<br />\n只可以話亞視陣除 係關成個制作事......"}]}